**Summary:** This documentation explains how to use session metrics (legacy metrics) like bounce rate and exit rate in Amplitude Analytics to evaluate content paths, specifically focusing on how grouping properties determine bounce classification and how these metrics are calculated only for active events in the Data Table chart under the Metrics tab.

